{"tid":1786630,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"主子四個月大.. 有D曳 大家有冇教貓主子既心得?","createTime":"2019-12-17T09:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T17:35:23.000Z","uid":1206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ceed6b9c72fa953915a3bca3ba8e539e499bb3fc","tid":1786630,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:23:54.000Z","msg":"我接左主子番黎一個月 由第一日到今日都好活躍<br />\n因為屋企係舊樓 所以有好多地方比佢跑跑跳跳 有晒貓樹比佢爬<br />\n佢都痴人 每日我放工番黎都會去塊珪藻土度反肚要人摸<br />\n但佢既曳野都好多 <br />\n推野落地 咬爛SOFA 依D都接受到 預左<br />\n但麻煩係....<br />\n1. 佢成日衝入廚房 (可能知道我日日o係廚房整雞比佢食...) 一入到去就搵地方LAY埋 大家都知廚房污糟 我都好唔想佢入去 (再加上佢依家有少少金錢癬.. 睇左醫生 搽緊藥膏 D毛都生番晒出黎 下個月再睇) <br />\n次次佢入完 我都抱住佢鬧佢幾句 再放佢入籠一陣<br />\n但佢都唔驚... 成日見我煮緊飯就入黎.....  廚房唔太通風 所以我平時盡量都開少少門煮...<br />\n<br />\n2. 都幾常咬人<br />\n我知道唔可以比貓貓咬慣人 但有時我R R下佢個肚仔 (佢反肚mode) 就會突然間比佢咬 當然係細力<br />\n又有時掃下佢背D毛 又會兩隻手捉住你隻手黎咬...<br />\n又鐘意咬人腳指...<br />\n好擔心佢咬慣... 第日就大獲...<br />\n一樣啦 都係鬧佢都無用 (我已經每日都有同佢玩 貓棒/老鼠玩具比佢追比佢咬 都無乜改善)<br />\n不過好在 佢好少發脾氣咁咬人 早排一日洗兩次耳仔 佢只會想走 而唔會咬人 所以多數咬人都係玩/摸<br />\n<br />\n大致上都係依兩個問題... 佢4個月大 唔敢比零食佢去教佢 所以唔太知道點教主子好....<br />\n本身睇左好多文話教主子做動作等等 咩都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家叫佢個名都10次得1次成功令佢望一望我... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3240ab3b6ae3c363e5ef072d430ffe7d434bcc2c","tid":1786630,"uid":1206,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:28:12.000Z","msg":"奉上主子圖<br />\n請笑納<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50iwUiN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50iwUiN.jpg&h=8cbac8eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b4bRUiP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb4bRUiP.jpg&h=e1ad67a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sh16Jcg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsh16Jcg.png&h=93d65bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZO2hPSh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZO2hPSh.jpg&h=d9bf7e53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1a509d87ab082107041291abad59dc4249e49bd","tid":1786630,"uid":263198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:28:35.000Z","msg":"咬人真係睇性格<br />\n屋企三隻貓由出世養大都唔會咬人<br />\n有時整佢細力咬個d唔計啦<br />\n不過大隻d應該都唔會再咬架啦"},{"pid":"976debf5b41aa11a0d75274249475e9d78443b07","tid":1786630,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278f3bf833f33f2c237945a8b48930dcf623e012","tid":1786630,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1a509d87ab082107041291abad59dc4249e49bd","tid":1786630,"uid":263198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:28:35.000Z","msg":"咬人真係睇性格<br />\n屋企三隻貓由出世養大都唔會咬人<br />\n有時整佢細力咬個d唔計啦<br />\n不過大隻d應該都唔會再咬架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:30:12.000Z","msg":"咁係咪即係無乜計...<br />\n我試過佢一咬就伸入少少手指諗住嚇佢<br />\n佢轉個頭又咬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢好似心情一high就咬"},{"pid":"0439ec6262345a91e00b4b95099e709e7b4c45d5","tid":1786630,"uid":239321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:32:31.000Z","msg":"我家主子咬我<br />\n我咬返她轉頭<br />\n大家互片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6e1fdb4540f2e87ae8d6cfd99f89b726b18de4","tid":1786630,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0439ec6262345a91e00b4b95099e70